00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,870
The end-of-the-world fireworks

4
00:01:19,039 --> 00:01:21,680
gave me a reason to apply for Hua Qing University again.

5
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,520
Tomorrow

6
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:25,079
is the opening exhibition of the robotics competition.

7
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:26,720
Would you like to come?

8
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:30,110
Don't push your luck here.

9
00:02:31,110 --> 00:02:32,440
We had a deal today.

10
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:35,270
Hanging out together was an accident.

11
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:36,750
Well then,

12
00:02:37,670 --> 00:02:39,320
you are gonna have to hang on a little longer,

13
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:42,030
cause I'm not giving up.

14
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,960
Xianxian.

15
00:02:46,550 --> 00:02:47,320
Su.

16
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:48,670
What are you doing here?

17
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,720
I tried to find you in your room.

18
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,910
Your roommate said you were out.

19
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,030
It was raining outside.

20
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:54,440
Hope you didn't get caught in the rain.

21
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:55,800
With me around,

22
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,829
she won't.

23
00:03:01,829 --> 00:03:04,160
Am I interrupting something?

24
00:03:04,550 --> 00:03:05,470
No.

25
00:03:05,670 --> 00:03:06,440
A little bit.

26
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:10,110
Well, how about you give us a minute, then?

27
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,000
Sorry.

28
00:03:13,390 --> 00:03:14,880
There's something about work

29
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:16,160
to discuss with Xianxian.

30
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,750
She's getting a little tired.

31
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,910
What about another day.

32
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:26,079
Su, it's okay.

33
00:03:26,270 --> 00:03:27,960
What do you need me for?

34
00:03:30,270 --> 00:03:31,110
Let's find a quiet place,

35
00:03:31,110 --> 00:03:32,829
that we can sit down to talk.

36
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,110
Okay.

37
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:35,440
Let's go.

38
00:03:42,270 --> 00:03:43,830
Xianxian, look over this.

39
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:48,000
This is...

40
00:04:02,070 --> 00:04:03,510
You're everywhere!

41
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:04,830
Good point.

42
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,790
What's wrong with me being a customer here?

43
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,640
Xianxian,

44
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,110
There was this comic book company in the Huai city,

45
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:29,640
who asked us to design an app.

46
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,790
It's almost done

47
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:33,070
and is about to be launched.

48
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,550
The Director Zhang of the comic book company,

49
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,110
asked me if I could recommend an artist.

50
00:04:37,350 --> 00:04:38,510
And I thought of you.

51
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:43,350
Tech companies make comic book apps, too?

52
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,720
Your company really does everything.

53
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,920
Yeah, because we are a startup company.

54
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,390
The boss wants to try various services.

55
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,040
He's got foresight.

56
00:04:54,230 --> 00:04:55,320
Thank you.

57
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,390
If he doesn't,

58
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:58,790
he wouldn't send me here to cooperate with Xianxian.

59
00:04:59,670 --> 00:05:01,070
You're right about that.

60
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,550
That could be the only common point

61
00:05:03,550 --> 00:05:05,320
that we share.

62
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:07,230
But,

63
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:10,670
I have no experience in

64
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,640
working on comic book apps like this.

65
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,070
Don't worry about this.

66
00:05:14,350 --> 00:05:16,480
This app is currently the first one in China.

67
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,510
and the only professional platform exclusively for comics.

68
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,390
I think it's quite good.

69
00:05:20,670 --> 00:05:22,600
I wonder if you're interested.

70
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,070
So what do I need to do?

71
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,040
It happens that we are currently in the Huai City,

72
00:05:28,350 --> 00:05:29,670
if you're interested,

73
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,070
come with me to see director Zhang tomorrow.

74
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:36,200
Tomorrow? Tomorrow is probably not okay.

75
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,830
Are you...

76
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,640
Are you going to see him?

77
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:44,720
No.

78
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:48,350
The show-stand for our comic club need to be prepared tomorrow.

79
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:50,510
I'm afraid I can't make time.

80
00:05:51,550 --> 00:05:52,390
Then...

81
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,720
I'll make arrangement when you are free.

82
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,830
That's great. Thank you, Su.

83
00:05:57,230 --> 00:05:58,160
So I'll take my leave now.

84
00:05:58,350 --> 00:06:00,040
I have to work on my sketch tonight.

85
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:01,830
Let me walk you to your place.

86
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:12,880
Don't we all stay in the same hotel here?

87
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:36,070
See you then. You don't have to walk me there.

88
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:38,510
Wait a minute.

89
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,600
I need to talk to you.

90
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,160
Could you please give us some privacy?

91
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:56,160
Su,

92
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:59,070
how about you go first?

93
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,760
Okay.

94
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,200
Remember to rest early.

95
00:07:05,550 --> 00:07:06,550
If there's anything,

96
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:07,790
call me at any time.

97
00:07:07,790 --> 00:07:09,230
Okay, Su, bye.

98
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,200
Bye.

99
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,270
Good night.

100
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,510
Go ahead.

101
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,480
To be honest,

102
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,350
I don't like this guy very much.

103
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,320
But,

104
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,830
what he just said,

105
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,880
sounds like a good opportunity.

106
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:34,920
It worth you consideration.

107
00:07:38,270 --> 00:07:40,070
You chose to do what you love,

108
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,720
I'll definitely stand behind you.

109
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:51,440
Then I'll go back to my room.

110
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,880
Don't forget to come to the robot exhibition opening tomorrow.

111
00:08:03,110 --> 00:08:04,830
I'll be waiting for you.

112
00:08:14,549 --> 00:08:15,760
Did you two make up?

113
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,710
We were never together.

114
00:08:19,710 --> 00:08:20,880
There can't be "make up".

115
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:24,880
Forget about that.

116
00:08:25,550 --> 00:08:27,000
You betrayed me!

117
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,150
You've been in the amusement park all day,

118
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,470
and earned a course from Professor Ye.

119
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,710
Couldn't ask for more.

120
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,470
Xianxian's not here yet?

121
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,030
How could it be？ It's late already.

122
00:08:57,350 --> 00:08:58,280
Hurry up.

123
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,230
Lou Feng.

124
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:07,670
You put this here first,

125
00:09:07,670 --> 00:09:09,280
then go upstairs to get tomorrow's schedule.

126
00:09:09,710 --> 00:09:11,670
And you need to check out tomorrow's costumes in the dressing room.

127
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:14,350
I have to go to the dressing room?

128
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,320
I'll go to the dressing room.

129
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:18,080
My work is done here anyway.

130
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,520
You're not going to the robot contest opening?

131
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:23,080
No time for chat. Just move.

132
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,110
Okay, see you then!

133
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,400
Xianxian, I love you!

134
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,350
Get the schedule, hurry up.

135
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:44,080
Sir, this truck is ready to go!

136
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:45,910
Are you guys ready?

137
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:46,760
In a minute,

138
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,590
everyone's going to the central exhibition hall to give speeches.

139
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,110
Could you wait for some minutes?

140
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,710
We need few more minutes.

141
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:54,230
How many plans are you gonna show?

142
00:09:55,110 --> 00:09:57,710
Let's go with one first.

143
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,200
Are you doing this or not?

144
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,470
You can start the show now.

145
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,910
Don't wait for me.

146
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:10,400
I'm sorry.

147
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:14,470
Without Xianxian,

148
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,960
you can still give the show of your robot.

149
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,550
Without her here,

150
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,790
there is no point in doing the show anymore.

151
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,280
Why don't you just go inside? It's fine.

152
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:40,110
So, one two three four five six...

153
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:49,110
Why is it locked?

154
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:55,350
I'll go to the dressing room. My work is done here anyway.

155
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:02,880
Anyone out there?

156
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,200
Someone's in here!

157
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:09,030
Good work. See you guys.

158
00:11:09,230 --> 00:11:10,670
Bye! Bye!

159
00:11:12,230 --> 00:11:14,280
Xing Lufei, I got the schedule.

160
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,150
Good.

161
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:18,710
Then we're done here today.

162
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,960
Good work.

163
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:21,440
So...

164
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,230
Where's Ding Xian?

165
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,520
Ding Xian is...

166
00:11:26,710 --> 00:11:28,400
She went to check out the dressing room,

167
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:31,840
and then I think there's something urgent, and she just left.

168
00:11:32,470 --> 00:11:33,470
Then I'll see you.

169
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,320
Bye.

170
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,200
Something urgent?

171
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:51,710
Boss,

172
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,670
The opening ceremony is over.

173
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,880
I don't think Xianxian will come.

174
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,590
Why don't we just go?

175
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:00,470
It's okay. You can go.

176
00:12:00,710 --> 00:12:01,550
You don't have to wait for me.

177
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,550
Okay, don't be too late.

178
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:09,030
No worries.

179
00:12:23,230 --> 00:12:27,470
Sir, why do you have Ding Xian's cell phone?

180
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,280
Oh, I'll fetch it right away.

181
00:12:31,030 --> 00:12:32,440
Wasn't she with you?

182
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,790
Don't tell me she is...

183
00:12:35,030 --> 00:12:36,880
still at the Comic-Con Center.

184
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,440
Ding Xian!

185
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:49,670
Ding Xian!

186
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:54,710
Ding Xian!

187
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,960
Ding Xian!

188
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:00,350
Zhou Siyue!

189
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,910
Zhou Siyue!

190
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,710
Zhou Siyue, I'm here!

191
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:09,080
Ding Xian!

192
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:12,280
I'm here. Can you hear me?

193
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,960
Ding Xian, are you in there?

194
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,440
I'm locked inside!

195
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:23,280
You step back a little!

196
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,400
Step back, okay?

197
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,030
Are you all right?

198
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:37,760
I'm okay.

199
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,150
Come.

200
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,400
Getting in here like this,

201
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:54,320
are you sure we won't get caught?

202
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,590
It's an emergency after all.

203
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,840
Just give me a second.

204
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:07,200
How did you get locked up in there?

205
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:09,080
I have no idea.

206
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:12,030
You have to be more careful from now on.

207
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:14,230
If I'm not around someday,

208
00:14:14,230 --> 00:14:15,230
what should you then?

209
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,200
Well...

210
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:20,550
I'm sure I'll get out the next day.

211
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:23,080
I could just wait for someone to open the door for me.

212
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:24,960
That's enough tough talk.

213
00:14:25,910 --> 00:14:26,960
Oh,

214
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,670
how was your opening ceremony?

215
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,280
I didn't do it.

216
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:32,520
Why?

217
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,080
Aren't you here,

218
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:36,790
just for the robot contest?

219
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:38,880
That's not entirely true.

220
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:41,960
I'm also here for you.

221
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,080
My little Lord Zhou,

222
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,320
when did you become so unambitious?

223
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,550
That's because,

224
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:57,350
I am sure enough that

225
00:14:58,470 --> 00:15:01,320
I can get the first place in the contest,

226
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:04,790
and I will get you too.

227
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,790
I'm leaving.

228
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,960
Why do you hate being with me so much?

229
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:17,670
Zhou Siyue,

230
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,910
when did you become such a scoundrel?

231
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:23,080
Maybe you should get to know me better.

232
00:15:25,350 --> 00:15:26,200
Come here.

233
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:28,790
Come here.

234
00:15:30,470 --> 00:15:32,320
Stay here and don't move.

235
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,230
Fellows, I'm leaving.

236
00:15:52,230 --> 00:15:54,400
I want to go away and look around.

237
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:56,230
Will you come back?

238
00:15:56,230 --> 00:15:58,640
I'll be back. Bye!

239
00:15:58,640 --> 00:15:59,910
Goodbye!

240
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:02,030
We'll wait for you to come back!

241
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:07,670
I'll miss you guys.

242
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:10,640
Don't you forget to miss me!

243
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:20,840
Help, help!

244
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:30,840
He's awake! Yes!

245
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:32,670
That's great!

246
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:51,190
I thought

247
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:53,640
that you never check Weibo.

248
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:56,190
"Little Monster Dairies"

249
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,560
Catchy name.

250
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:11,160
Ding Xian,

251
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:13,520
you once asked me

252
00:17:14,470 --> 00:17:16,160
what is true love.

253
00:17:17,350 --> 00:17:19,350
Now I know the answer.

254
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,950
Her look seems ordinary,

255
00:17:25,950 --> 00:17:27,880
yet I finding her beautiful day by day.

256
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:31,070
It's like...

257
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,710
she is so stubborn that almost makes in rage

258
00:17:35,310 --> 00:17:36,400
and yet making me feel,

259
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:39,560
she is the cutest in the world.

260
00:17:41,190 --> 00:17:43,070
It's like knowing that she's lying,

261
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,350
and yet,

262
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:47,560
I just couldn't spoil her poor acting.

263
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,070
It's like...

264
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:56,640
always crying like a mess,

265
00:17:58,590 --> 00:18:00,310
and yet she is still attractive.

266
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:05,040
You're a mess.

267
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:08,430
Who is that

268
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,160
you are talking about?

269
00:18:16,190 --> 00:18:17,280
Ding Xian,

270
00:18:20,470 --> 00:18:21,760
I love you.

271
00:18:24,830 --> 00:18:26,760
Would you be my girlfriend?

272
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,560
What are you doing here?

273
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:49,680
Who let you in?

274
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:59,280
How did you get in here?

275
00:19:00,190 --> 00:19:01,760
Now you people don't even give a shit

276
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:03,230
about us security guards anymore?

277
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:04,880
Put down your information!

278
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:08,710
We're sorry.

279
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:11,280
I brought her there.

280
00:19:11,710 --> 00:19:13,830
So, it has nothing to do with her.

281
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:17,430
You young lovers nowadays...

282
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:19,230
Must you have to seek thrills?

283
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:21,760
Write. What are you looking at?

284
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:23,880
Just write, everything!

285
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,640
We're not lovers.

286
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:29,040
Look at your good-looking face,

