00:19:29,230 --> 00:19:31,230
how come you can't even get a girl?

288
00:19:34,230 --> 00:19:35,920
I was working on it.

289
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:38,560
And then you cut me off.

290
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:40,430
Y'all wait here for a sec.

291
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,430
I'll go for a check.

292
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:43,000
You can't leave until everything's clear.

293
00:19:53,760 --> 00:19:55,190
You haven't given me an answer yet.

294
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,280
Zhou Siyue,

295
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:01,280
I'm sorry.

296
00:20:02,470 --> 00:20:05,590
I'm not planning on a relationship.

297
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:10,680
Gee, you,

298
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:12,880
you sure can hold a grudge.

299
00:20:15,190 --> 00:20:16,000
Fine,

300
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,710
I'll be waiting for you.

301
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:22,190
I'll wait for your answer.

302
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,710
Xianxian.

303
00:20:27,430 --> 00:20:28,470
why are you here?

304
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:30,040
Su.

305
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,310
Mr. Su, what brings you here?

306
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:36,830
You know them?

307
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,590
They're my friends.

308
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:40,710
Here.

309
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,430
Thank you.

310
00:20:43,430 --> 00:20:45,430
That's it. You can leave now.

311
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:46,400
Don't do that again.

312
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,560
Mr. Su, see you then.

313
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:49,800
Good work.

314
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:54,110
Why are you here?

315
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,350
The contest starts tomorrow.

316
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:58,310
I'm here to check the procedures with the organizer.

317
00:20:59,710 --> 00:21:00,800
Are you going back to the hotel?

318
00:21:00,950 --> 00:21:01,880
I can give you a ride.

319
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,230
Sure.

320
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,560
Thank you.

321
00:21:17,950 --> 00:21:19,040
Xianxian,

322
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:21,040
your mom called me the other day.

323
00:21:21,190 --> 00:21:22,560
She asked me to take good care of you,

324
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:23,800
since we are both in the Huai City now.

325
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:25,710
I'm a little busy these days,

326
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,880
when I'm done, I'll take you out for fun.

327
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,190
Mr. Su, you're so busy,

328
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:35,040
maybe we should forget about these social courtesies.

329
00:21:38,230 --> 00:21:39,400
That's where you're wrong.

330
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:42,000
For me, Xianxian was never a courtesy.

331
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,000
She always sees me as a brother, too.

332
00:21:46,190 --> 00:21:47,110
Does she?

333
00:21:47,590 --> 00:21:49,830
Then how come I have never heard her mention

334
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,470
you, her big brother?

335
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:57,880
Maybe it's because you two

336
00:21:57,880 --> 00:21:59,230
were never that close?

337
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:03,070
It's no wonder that you didn't know.

338
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,230
Of course Xianxian wouldn't tell you.

339
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:07,830
She wouldn't tell anything to a stranger.

340
00:22:08,230 --> 00:22:10,470
Even if she doesn't tell me anything,

341
00:22:11,070 --> 00:22:12,640
I know what she likes,

342
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:13,800
and what she dislikes.

343
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:33,230
Xianxian,

344
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:35,280
I want to talk to you,

345
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:36,760
about the comic book app.

346
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:38,800
What is it?

347
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,830
Do you mind giving us a minute?

348
00:22:45,280 --> 00:22:47,160
It's not a secret.

349
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,760
Can't you talk in front of me?

350
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:54,160
It's okay, Su. Go ahead.

351
00:22:55,590 --> 00:22:57,310
Director Zhang of the comic book company

352
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:59,470
saw your works on your Weibo, and liked them very much.

353
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,310
He's having a dinner tomorrow,

354
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:02,950
and wants to sign the contract with you in person.

355
00:23:03,190 --> 00:23:05,560
That's great. Thank you so much, Su.

356
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:06,590
I didn't do much.

357
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:07,710
I just introduced you.

358
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:09,590
I'll take you shopping for some clothes tomorrow.

359
00:23:09,950 --> 00:23:11,640
It's better to dress formally.

360
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:14,470
What's wrong with her clothes?

361
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:21,350
It's okay, Su.

362
00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:23,040
I have clothes.

363
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,190
Don't worry.

364
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:28,190
Okay then, I'll go with you tomorrow.

365
00:23:28,430 --> 00:23:29,560
Don't be nervous.

366
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,760
Ding Xian won't be nervous.

367
00:23:33,190 --> 00:23:34,710
You don't know her very well.

368
00:23:40,830 --> 00:23:42,190
I'll see you then.

369
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:50,760
Zhou Siyue,

370
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:53,070
I have told you,

371
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:56,560
stay away from Xianxian.

372
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,680
I have told you too,

373
00:24:00,590 --> 00:24:02,400
I won't let go.

374
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:13,950
So that's all for today's discussion,

375
00:24:14,520 --> 00:24:16,470
I hope that in the contest,

376
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:17,880
we'll all have a good performance.

377
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:19,310
Thank you all.

378
00:24:25,430 --> 00:24:26,400
Awake now?

379
00:24:29,470 --> 00:24:30,760
You took notes?

380
00:24:31,830 --> 00:24:33,040
Good for you.

381
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,350
Career, love,

382
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:36,640
acing in both.

383
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:42,400
Look at him,

384
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:44,160
what a social butterfly.

385
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:46,070
Talking to everyone.

386
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:52,160
Come on, it's none of your business.

387
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,190
Let's go.

388
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:55,760
Where are you going?

389
00:24:58,760 --> 00:24:59,920
Comic-Con.

390
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,880
Maybe you shouldn't go.

391
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:04,710
Why?

392
00:25:05,280 --> 00:25:06,830
Because Xianxian is not there.

393
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,880
How do you know that she's not there?

394
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:11,590
I asked Lou Feng and she told me.

395
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:13,800
Then where is she?

396
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,590
She's...

397
00:25:18,830 --> 00:25:21,760
she's taken back to the hotel by Su Bocong.

398
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:28,310
Xianxian, how was your show today?

399
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:29,560
It went well.

400
00:25:29,710 --> 00:25:31,160
And there were a lot of people.

401
00:25:31,310 --> 00:25:32,400
I finished just now.

402
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,000
So you haven't eaten all day?

403
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:37,400
- I'm used to it. I'm not hungry. - Ding Xian!

404
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,070
Why didn't you answer my call?

405
00:25:49,950 --> 00:25:51,400
My cell phone is dead.

406
00:25:53,110 --> 00:25:56,070
Weren't you at the academic conference?

407
00:25:56,230 --> 00:25:57,950
Why are you back so soon?

408
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,560
It's over.

409
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:02,000
Don't you have a speech to prepare?

410
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,160
I pulled an all-nighter and finished it last night.

411
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:05,710
Then you should go back to your room and catch some sleep.

412
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:06,950
What are you doing here?

413
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,830
I wanna see you.

414
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:17,640
Mr. Zhou, you are really everywhere.

415
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:18,830
Can't seem to lose you.

416
00:26:18,950 --> 00:26:19,880
Right back at you.

417
00:26:20,710 --> 00:26:21,590
Mr. Su.

418
00:26:22,190 --> 00:26:24,520
You're probably not in a position to laugh at me.

419
00:26:32,070 --> 00:26:33,400
Anyone wants some juice?

420
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:34,830
- I'll get it. - I'll get it.

421
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,230
No, no, no, I'll go.

422
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:39,880
- Stay here. - Stay here.

423
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:43,590
Waiter, a glass of juice please.

424
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:44,830
What kind of juice would you like?

425
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:46,000
- Blueberry. - Blueberry.

426
00:26:47,830 --> 00:26:48,710
Hot or cold?

427
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:49,800
- Cold. - Cold.

428
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,800
And sweetness?

429
00:26:52,950 --> 00:26:53,950
- Full sweetness. - Full sweetness.

430
00:26:59,110 --> 00:27:00,110
One cup?

431
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:01,590
One cup each.

432
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:04,680
I'll pay for mine, and he pay by himself.

433
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,430
Okay.

434
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:17,590
Thank you.

435
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:26,710
This is too much. I can't drink this much.

436
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:39,400
Xianxian, you must be hungry.

437
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,070
What about have a dinner together before we go back?

438
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,470
Okay.

439
00:27:44,110 --> 00:27:45,710
Mr. Su, you treated me last time.

440
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,830
I feel quite embarrassed.

441
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,470
I'll pay this time.

442
00:27:49,190 --> 00:27:50,590
I haven't said yes yet.

443
00:27:50,590 --> 00:27:51,430
Sure.

444
00:27:51,950 --> 00:27:53,560
Why don't we call up everyone?

445
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,800
We haven't had dinner together yet in the Huai City, anyway.

446
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:57,880
I know a place that is quite good.

447
00:27:58,470 --> 00:27:59,560
However,

448
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:01,880
Mr. Zhou, I'm afraid it's gonna cost you.

449
00:28:03,110 --> 00:28:04,400
Don't worry about me.

450
00:28:04,710 --> 00:28:05,590
You should worry about

451
00:28:06,040 --> 00:28:08,560
whether you stand a chance anymore.

452
00:28:12,950 --> 00:28:13,920
Too sour.

453
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:23,640
See you around.

454
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,830
You're back.

455
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:40,230
What is this?

456
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:41,430
Blueberry juice.

457
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,680
No, thanks. It's too sour.

458
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:48,950
Rumors had it, two cute guys

459
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,070
went for you at the same time today.

460
00:28:51,280 --> 00:28:52,470
Tell me tell me,

461
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:55,160
are you super happy today?

462
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,830
How is that possible?

463
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,640
They are two big babies!

464
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,680
I am so annoyed.

465
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:04,400
Anyway,

466
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:08,310
I'm still rooting the CP of you and Zhou Siyue.

467
00:29:09,070 --> 00:29:11,400
You liked him for so many years.

468
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:14,470
If you can't be together,

469
00:29:15,590 --> 00:29:17,400
it'd be such a huge shame.

470
00:29:19,040 --> 00:29:20,190
Actually,

471
00:29:21,830 --> 00:29:23,950
he asked me If I would be his girlfriend.

472
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:27,470
I almost said yes.

473
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,230
You refused?

474
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:32,040
I liked him for so many years.

475
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:34,280
And he's only been after me for a few days.

476
00:29:34,470 --> 00:29:36,470
If I just say yes so easily,

477
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,680
I'll be completely controlled by him

478
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,920
in the future.

479
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,310
You have a point.

480
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,040
But,

481
00:29:45,470 --> 00:29:47,800
I always feel that something is missing

482
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:49,560
between the two of us.

483
00:29:50,110 --> 00:29:51,280
What is missing?

484
00:29:52,190 --> 00:29:53,190
I don't know.

485
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:55,560
I can't figure it out.

486
00:30:00,230 --> 00:30:01,000
Is she going?

487
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:04,800
It's his treat this the evening.

488
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,190
Are you going?

489
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:09,310
Forget it. I'm not.

490
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,190
Come now!

491
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,950
I'll go out for a while.

492
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:26,470
Bocong,

493
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:28,680
why didn't you go inside?

494
00:30:29,230 --> 00:30:30,680
I want to tell you something.

495
00:30:31,350 --> 00:30:32,590
What is it?

496
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:34,070
Here's the thing.

497
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:36,190
I know that you like Ding Xian.

498
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:37,470
I can help you.

499
00:30:40,470 --> 00:30:41,800
Why are you helping me?

500
00:30:43,430 --> 00:30:44,680
For Zhou Siyue?

501
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:48,110
Well, they're not together yet.

502
00:30:48,310 --> 00:30:49,760
I still have a chance. So do you.

503
00:30:58,710 --> 00:30:59,350
Lou Feng,

504
00:30:59,350 --> 00:31:01,470
did you forget something again?

505
00:31:01,470 --> 00:31:02,470
You're so...

506
00:31:06,110 --> 00:31:07,350
Why are you here?

507
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,310
To take you to dinner.

508
00:31:09,470 --> 00:31:10,430
I'm not hungry.

509
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:20,470
You don't want to see me?

510
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:23,920
Don't flatter yourself.

511
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:28,310
I'm buying dinner for everyone because of you.

512
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:31,280
I can't believe you're not even coming.

513
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:34,040
I didn't ask for that.

514
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,590
Anyway, I'll starve myself here if you won't go.

515
00:31:37,190 --> 00:31:38,230
I'm not leaving.

516
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:41,830
Fine, I'll go.

517
00:31:42,350 --> 00:31:43,230
I'll go eat.

518
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:50,160
Welcome!

519
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:52,470
Xianxian.

520
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:53,400
Here.

521
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:55,760
Xianxian, this way, I saved you a seat.

522
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:56,950
Okay.

523
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,640
Zhou Siyue, sit here.

524
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:02,680
Boss, here.

525
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:05,760
I'm telling you,

526
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,520
we've been here for so many days,

527
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:09,520
and didn't get the chance to get together, right?

528
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:11,640
Today, my boss pays the bill.

529
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,560
Just order anything you want, cheers!

530
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:14,710
Okay, thank you, Prince Charming.

531
00:32:14,830 --> 00:32:16,110
You're welcome.

532
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:17,760
Just enjoy yourself.

533
00:32:17,950 --> 00:32:18,950
Here, order the food.

534
00:32:25,070 --> 00:32:26,640
Thank you.

535
00:32:30,310 --> 00:32:31,590
I want this.

536
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,830
Thank you, handsome.

537
00:32:36,190 --> 00:32:38,280
Nice that we're together here today.

538
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:39,430
Let's not just eat.

539
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:40,640
How about playing a game?

540
00:32:41,110 --> 00:32:43,430
Which game? Just the one we used to play.

541
00:32:43,430 --> 00:32:44,710
The King game.

542
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,230
I brought the cards. Here.

543
00:32:46,470 --> 00:32:48,680
You are all prepared.

544
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,520
Of course.

545
00:32:50,590 --> 00:32:51,590
Do you know how to play?

546
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:52,880
I don't know.

547
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:54,110
Here, I'll deal.

548
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,070
It's okay. I'll teach you.

549
00:32:58,830 --> 00:32:59,830
Pass it on.

550
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,430
First hand, who's the king?

551
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:05,070
I am the king.

552
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:07,000
My order is simple.

553
00:33:07,280 --> 00:33:09,400
Give me a toast, and call me gorgeous.

554
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:10,560
That'll do.

555
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:12,190
Who do you want? Right. What's the number?

556
00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:13,160
What's the number? What's the number?

557
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:15,430
Number two.

558
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:17,310
Number two. Who's number two? Who's number two?

559
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:19,070
Who is number two?

560
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,350
Gorgeous, to you.

561
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:28,950
What? I can't hear you.

562
00:33:28,950 --> 00:33:29,760
What?

563
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:32,760
Ban Jiayu, sorry.

564
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:35,560
You gorgeous, here to you!

565
00:33:37,110 --> 00:33:38,590
Drink it up! Up, up.

566
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,120
Drink up. You're good.

567
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:46,870
Well done.

568
00:33:46,870 --> 00:33:47,760
Nice.

569
00:33:48,320 --> 00:33:49,429
Go on, go on.

570
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:57,800
